description:
Danny chats about the first episode of The Hills reboot! Barbara Kavovit (author of Heels of Steel) from The Real Housewives of New York also calls in to talk about this season, her hot mic moment, the spray tan she left behind in Miami, and so much more!


Barbara K. Interview: 26:40ish
